  Cell["Analytical Helmholtz decomposition of n-dimensional vector fields, \
following Richters and Glotzl (2023).", "GuideAbstract"], 
  Cell["Decomposing a vector field", "GuideFunctionsSection"], 
  Cell["HelmholtzDecomposition", "InlineFunctionSans"], 
  Cell["    construct the decomposition object f = g + r and access derived \
